# TensorFlow Serving Model Directory
#
# Models are downloaded at deploy time by scripts/tf-model-download.sh.
# They are NOT committed to git due to size (4 models ≈ 15 GB total).
#
# Models served:
#   - whisper/1/        OpenAI Whisper Large-v3 (ASR, ~10 GB GPU)
#   - sam2/1/           Meta SAM2 Hiera-Large (segmentation, ~7.5 GB GPU)
#   - realesrgan/1/     Real-ESRGAN 4x (super-resolution, ~5 GB GPU)
#   - mobilenet_v2/1/   MobileNetV2 1.0-224 (classification, ~0.5 GB)
#
# To download models:
#   ./scripts/tf-model-download.sh
#   or: docker compose -f docker-compose.tensorflow.yml run --rm model-download
#
# Model registry: services/pre-processing/tf_models/model_registry.yaml
